title: Starts of the Week + Week 6 Breakdown, Bye-pocalypse is Coming! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/14
description:
It’s football time! Week 6 is here and The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason dive into Week 6 matchups and reveal their Starts of the Week! Plus, injury updates, and a new edition of “Never Not Working!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 14th, 2021.
  
 (04:15) - Never Not Working
 (09:55) - NFL News 
 (15:05) - Fantasy Forecast
 (15:50) - Dolphins at Jaguars
 (20:25) - Packers at Bears
 (27:35) - Bengals at Lions
 (33:50) - Texans at Colts
 (36:55) - Rams at Giants
 (39:40) - Chiefs at Washington Football Team
 (44:45) - Vikings at Panthers
 (48:25) - Starts of the Week
 (48:30) - QB Starts of the Week
 (52:10) - RB Starts of the Week
 (54:05) - WR Starts of the Week
 (56:40) - TE Starts of the Week
 (59:30) - Boom Boom Kicker of the Week
